## Why This Is Asked

This ensures scalable, fair CKNE-driven caching across many tenants, balancing latency and hit rate in real time.

## Key Concepts

- CKNE-to-quota mapping with a guaranteed baseline
- CKNE-aware eviction policy (weighted LFU/LRU) plus selective prefetch
- Minute-by-minute rebalancing with safety guards and observability

## Code Example

```javascript
function computeQuotas(totSlots, tenants){
  const total = tenants.reduce((s,t)=>s+t.ckne,0);
  return tenants.map(t=>{
    const w = Math.max(0.05, t.ckne);
    const q = Math.max(1, Math.round((w/total)*totSlots));
    return {tenant: t.tenant, quota: q};
  });
}
```

