## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to translate CKNE into concrete cache resource management with safety constraints and telemetry.

## Key Concepts

- CKNE-to-cache-slot mapping
- Per-minute rebalancing with rate limits
- TTL eviction and stale-data risk

## Code Example

```javascript
// Pseudocode: compute per-tenant quota from CKNE weight
function computeQuota(ckne, totalSlots, baseline) {
  const weight = ckne;
  const quota = Math.max(1, Math.round(baseline + (totalSlots - baseline) * weight));
  return quota;
}
```

